#: [[歐洲]][[中古]][[時代]][[進前]][[的]]Skandinavia[[會使講]][[是]][[歐洲]][[文明]][[的]]'''草地'''，[[並]][[無]][[受著]]Roma[[帝國]][[管轄]][[抑是]][[影響]]。 (''[[Traditional Chinese|trad.]]'')
#: [[欧洲]][[中古]][[时代]][[进前]][[的]]Skandinavia[[会使讲]][[是]][[欧洲]][[文明]][[的]]'''草地'''，[[并]][[无]][[受着]]Roma[[帝国]][[管辖]][[抑是]][[影响]]。 (''[[Simplified Chinese|simp.]]'')
#: ''{{unicode|Au-chiu Tiong-kó· Sî-tāi chìn-chêng ê Skandinavia ē-sái kóng sī Au-chiu bûn-bêng ê '''chháu-tē''', pēng-bô siū tio̍h Roma Tè-kok koán-hat a̍h-sī éng-hióng}}.''
#: ''It can be said that [[Scandinavia]], prior to the European [[Middle Ages]], was a '''rural area''' within European [[civilization]], and had not been governed or influenced by the Roman empire.''

